                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/980" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0089</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9899 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信银行信用卡中心T计划项目打造企业内部人才永动机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">T Plan Project Practiced in Credit Card Center of China CITIC Bank as an Engine to Promote Internal </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷善玉，刘惠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信银行信用卡中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">T计划项目；培训培训师；胜任力模型；精神激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">T Plan Project; Training the Trainer; Competence Model; Mental Encouragement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">      中信银行信用卡中心业务的快速发展，对相关人才的系统性和可持续性的培养方面提出了更高的要求。为了解决此问题，该中心及时实施了“培训培训师”的T计划项目。
    本案例描述了中信银行信用卡中心的T计划项目是从内训师的内部严格选拔、提升培训能力和发展规划等各个方面入手，通过一系列体系建设，激励内训师热爱培训工作，让他们在传承奉献的同时，也获得更好的职业发展，使他们感受到自我价值实现和被尊重的需要，解决了内训师发展的长久性和稳定性问题。
    另外T计划项目将企业培训与发展战略紧密结合起来，通过对内训师的培训和培养，提高并更新整个中心的员工业务水平和能力，满足了迅速增长的业务发展需要和客户日益提高了的服务需求，最终让培训更好地帮助了企业发展。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">    Rapid business development of China CITIC Bank’s Credit Card Center (CCC) put forward higher requirements for keeping talents training more systemic and sustainable, and CCC promptly practiced T Plan Project to “train the trainer” for dealing with this problem. 
    This case described that T Plan Project of CCC was performed by constructing a series of systems including strict internal trainers selection, training skills improvement and trainers development plan to stimulate internal trainers to increase their job passion, enjoy their better vocational development during the process of their teaching and devotion, it would make trainer enjoy the experience that their self-worth were realized and their being required were respected, and it contributed internal trainers’ development with long term stability.
    In addition, T Plan Project tightly integrated organizational training system with its development strategy, and through training and developing the internal trainers, it improved and renewed professional business level and abilities of the whole CCC’s employees, satisfied the requirements for rapid business development and customers’ increasing service, and it finally made training systems to develop firms better.   </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》、</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">精神激励、岗位需求的胜任能力、企业内训师体系、精细化管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-10</td>
                            </tr>
